title: Little Penguins
author: Britterzbee
pages:
Little penguins, blue
penguins or fairy
penguins are a
species of tiny
penguins that live
around the southern
coast of Australia.
They are absolutely
tiny (only about 33 cm
or 13 in in height) and
super cute. I don't
believe they're
dangerous but
knowing australia

they're probably like
venomous and super
vicious or something.
